| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1060 — Recovery Inhibition (thegentlemen)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: be0042e4-2fbb-5457-84ea-2c8fa44bff48"
